======================================================================

sigma_3(n) through the tournament lens:

  sigma_3( 1) =        1
  sigma_3( 2) =        9 = KEY2^2
  sigma_3( 3) =       28 = C(8,2) = C(rank(E8),2)
  sigma_3( 4) =       73
  sigma_3( 5) =      126 = C(9,4)
